Subject: [PATCH 20/20] media: Remove wait_{prepare, finish}
Date: Thu, 24 May 2018 17:35:20 -0300
Message-Id: <20180524203520.1598-21-ezequiel@collabora.com>
In-Reply-To: <20180524203520.1598-1-ezequiel@collabora.com>
References: <20180524203520.1598-1-ezequiel@collabora.com>
Sender: linux-media-owner@vger.kernel.org
List-ID: <linux-media.vger.kernel.org>

Now that all drivers provide a proper vb2_queue lock,
and that wait_{prepare, finish} are no longer in use,
get rid of them.

Signed-off-by: Ezequiel Garcia <ezequiel@collabora.com>
